1. If you want to have several sections on your web page and wish to have them a specfici height or even the entire view height,
then use the vh property like below. this section will take up 95% of the view height of the particualr section.
.section{
  height: 95vh;
  background-image: linear-gradient(to right bottom,rgba(126, 213, 111, 0.8), rgba(40, 180, 131, 0.8)),url(../img/hero.jpg);
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: top;
}
